## How the Tiers Work

The wizard has **three tiers** of questions. After each tier, execute the corresponding recipe **immediately** before moving to the next tier. This lets the user stop at any tier boundary and continue later.

At each tier boundary, ask: **"Ready for the next round, or want to stop here and continue later?"**

If the user stops early, tell them which tier they completed and what's left.

