## Tier 1: Identity & Branding

**Ask these questions first** (present conversationally, not as a wall of text):

1. **App name?** — Used in title bar, emails, auth pages, PWA manifest, sidebar, everywhere. (Default: Sourdough)
2. **Short name / abbreviation?** — 1-3 characters for collapsed sidebar and PWA icon text. (Default: SD)
3. **One-line description?** — For README, meta tags, PWA manifest description.
4. **Primary brand color?** — Hex code, color name, or "describe it." (Default: `#3b82f6` blue)
5. **Font style preference?** — Show this table:

