## Resuming

If the user returns and says "Get cooking" again (or "continue setup", "resume cooking"), check what has already been done:
- If app name is no longer "Sourdough" → Tier 1 is done
- If features have been removed → Tier 2 is done
- If git history has been reset → Tier 3 is done

Pick up from the next incomplete tier.

